description: Even on All Hallows' Eve, ghoulies and ghosties and long-leggedy beasties stand no chance against intrepid heroes and explorers armed with the latest steam-driven technology...or do they? Will phantoms of phlogiston fall before the stalwarts of steam, or will they be bold enough to best the brass and glass?
name: Steambusters

deck: Featuring some of the super teen teams finest and most influential adventures in the 50 years of their creation.
name: Teen Titans: A Celebration of 50 Years

volume.name: Teen Titans: A Celebration of 50 Years

deck: A collection for sports fans and nostalgia buffs

description: Who exactly are the Dream Police? Where do they come from? How are prospective officers chosen? Those seem like fairly straightforward questions...except that they are cover for a secret that goes back to the beginnings of civilization, a secret that must be protected at all costs, especially from the inquiries of Lieutenant Detective Joe Thursday. Joe has always been a loyal member of the Dream Police...but when his instincts as a cop tell him that the people he's working for are aligning against him, how far will he go to find the truth about them?
Alex and Ada must find a resolution.

The best-selling graphic novels series 100 BULLETS written by Brian Azzarello and illustrated by Eduardo Risso is now re-collected in a five volume series!

This dark and intriguing Eisner Award-winning series features a mysterious agent named Graves who approaches ordinary citizens and gives them an opportunity to exact revenge on a person who has wronged them. Offering his clients an attaché case containing proof of the deed and a gun, he guarantees his "clients" full immunity for all of their actions, including murder.

This volume collects 100 Bullets #1-19.
name: Book One

description: Wonder Woman allows an otherdimensional science-villain to capture her, but his android slaves throw a wrench in her plan to save the day!
name: No Chains Can Hold Her! Part 1

description: A tense hostage situation leads Team Arrow to discover that Brother Blood may still be alive! But how many acolytes does the Church of Blood have? And what is their plan for Starling City?
name: Blood: Ascension

description: King Tut is back, and his newly discovered Osirus Virus threatens to turn the good citizens of Gotham into his mindless slaves!
name: Chapter Forty-Seven

description: The final chapter of Pandora's origin story.

As the now radioactive Hurricane Brandon begins to fight back, Cale is forced to admit to the Project Zephyr team that he is ultimately to blame for the disaster. Now it is a race against time to out think his meteorological doppelgänger before it destroys him and the entire continent.

Because of the blatant attack on his castle, Lord Yukimura Sanada sends three of his Brave 10 warriors on a reconnaissance mission to Izumo. Empowered by being named a Sanada Brave, Isanami embarks on this journey with haste. Along the way Isanami is met with flesh-hungry wolves, and she discovers that she may be more than just a mere shrine maiden. Following this fearful discovery, Isanami is kidnapped by a malicious thief! Will our heroes survive these seemingly ill-fated circumstances? If they do, and with the Date warriors on their tail, what exactly is waiting for them in Izumo?

Chapter Titles

  • Act.6: Six Braves
  • Act.7: An Extraordinary Girl
  • Act.8: The Eye of A Typhoon
  • Act.9: The Crazy Climber
  • Act.10: Confidence
  • Act.11: The Dark Lord
name: Vol. 2

description: Acclaimed and NYT Bestselling author Charlaine Harris, the writer of the Sookie Stackhouse series, has joined the Dynamite Entertainment family with the first book of her hit Harper Connelly series, Grave Sight. Charlaine's Sookie Stackhouse novels became the basis for one of today's most successful television shows, the hit HBO series True Blood! Dynamite is extremely proud to present Charlaine Harris' first comic adaptation! This is chapter 3 of the the hit 2011 limited series presented digitally in 6 parts.
name: Chapter Three

description: Charlie McCarthy was one of the most popular enteratinment acts of the 1950's. Charlie's adventures are brought to life in his every own comic book series. Two stories in one! Charlie and Mortimer track down two criminals that have escaped from jail and Charlie makes a baby alligator his pet. Charlie McCarthy and Gladstone the Alligator Cast of Characters.

The life of Christ continues as he heals the centurion's servant, the resurrection at Nain, demons cast from Mary, the beheading of John the Baptist, amd the parable of the soils. Addendum: " THE GIFT"
name: Volume 5: The Deliverer

description:
Act Three

While the young couple's relationship blooms, a young man seeks solace through reconnecting to past associates, with dire consequences.
name: Act Three

description: From James Tynion IV (writer of DC's TALON) and digital pioneer Jeremy Rock comes a new political horror thriller! There's something monstrous going on in Washington, D.C.--and the repercussions could affect the balance of world power!
name: Chapter 7

description: The Endling unleashes his full powers at the lab, but can he escape the sim?

Amarosa has survived her first trial but the next may be more than she can handle. Amarosa will confront a fear she had lost but has regained in a new fashion as she braves a fight against a colossal robot responsible for the eradication of the human race.

Note: The digital edition (11/12/2014) for this issue was released before the print edition.
name: Rock 'Em, Sock 'Em

description:
CHAPTER FOUR -

Beneath Stonehenge, Hank gets some answers about what may be happening to him. Meanwhile, in Antarctica, Singh's revelation causes further unrest, as thing quickly spiral out of control.

Who Am I

The desert is a place where questions go to die. Follow The Girl as she begins her search for answers, a search that will ultimately bring her...home.
name: Who Am I

volume.name: A Girl Walks Home Alone at Night

description: With their plane shot down by Dark Bird's new, top-secret, invincible craft Ace and Penny find themselves hanging by a thread over a deep crevice. A botched self-rescue attempt leaves Ace injured, and Penny has to use all her wits and skill to save her new husband. If only she could shake these hallucinations of Skippy saying how she'll care for Ace once Penny's gone!

The Heroes Club take it upon themselves to explore an abandoned house in their neighborhood that they think could be haunted...but who they find lurking behind the door will shock them to their very core! Let the action...BEGIN!
name: Halloween Hijinx Part Two

description: High above the Earth, Celine is trapped by the mysterious Stormbreakers while deep below the ground, Tuck attempts to free himself from the leader of the Orphans, He-Who-Burns. The kids don't just have to reunite with each other-unless they get these two groups to stop warring and work together, their world is doomed!
Galahad finally crosses the line with Nocturnus. Their rekindled partnership ends before it can even really begin--but Nocturnus finds a new ally.

Betrayed, bloody, and mad as hell, it's Jack's turn to go on the hunt, sucking chest wound or no. But Jack hasn't even met the man called Usurper face-to-face and he's already fighting for his live. With both Jack and Ramona's lives on the line, who will go down for the count?

Note: The digital edition (11/12/2014) for this issue was released before the print edition.
name: Part Two

description: A frantic rescue effort continues. Can the Russian Navy save its K-141 Kursk?
name: Chapter 3

description: He's mean, he's green, and sometimes he's too small to be seen - he's the Incredible Hulk! Yes, the Hulk's back in another round of tales full of trials, tribulations, revenge, romance and... Richard Nixon?! Returning from a battle with Dr. Doom, the Hulk finds himself in the sights of the U.S. military's Project: Greenskin. Objective? Destroy the Hulk! The adventure continues with the green girl of Hulk's heart, the other-dimensional Jarella! With the help of Ant-Man, Hulk will reunite with his love - but not before he's put on trial in front of the heroes of the Marvel Universe! With art by the classic Herb Trimpe/John Severin team, Hulk's never looked meaner, greener or better! Collecting INCREDIBLE HULK (1968) #145-156.
name: Volume Eight

description: Featuring screen-capture images from MARVEL'S AVENGERS ASSEMBLE! Earth's Mightiest Heroes, the Avengers, explode onto the scene with action-packed, all-ages adventures! When the fiendish Attuma sends monsters and a giant tidal wave to sink the island of Manhattan, Hulk must prove that he is the strongest one there is or perish!? The Red Skull has turned the Avengers into rampaging monsters! Now, Hulk and Black Widow must team up and stop the raging Hulk-Vengers! The Impossible Man turns the Falcon into a movie star?! But the Chitauri have arrived to settle a score with Impossible Man! It's action aplenty from your favorite heroes, based on the hit animated series now airing on Disney XD! Collecting MARVEL UNIVERSE AVENGERS ASSEMBLE #9-12.
name: Volume 3

description: Morgan's learning that there are some definite upsides to being a teen-aged super-type -- like riding the original winged horse, PEGASUS! Unfortunately, the downsides include stuff like a mundane museum field trip turning deadly when the savage she-spider ARACHNE comes to call! Guest-starring THE ODYSSEY's super-strong SIGMA!

Baron's Crossing

Next Town Over's fourth chapter, in which Hunter tries to find a hot bath in picturesque milltown Baron's Crossing while Vane devises a devastating new weapon.
name: Baron's Crossing

description:
Taylor Martin and her disparate companions have survived a deadly virus outbreak. But are they the only ones?

With supplies running low, and tension running high, they're going to have to venture out into the seemingly abandoned city...
Tina the Warrior princess is pregnant, and her slacker wizard husband Pewfell, after having accidentally blown up his study, must take a job with the city sewer patrol in order to pay the bills.

Revelations

This issue marks the first appearance of Doctor Anarchy! A villain with telepathic, telekinetic, and emotion controlling powers. Can Shadowflame defeat a man who can kill with a thought? Only one way to find out! Also, making a special appearance in this chapter is Naser Subashi's smash hit girl Desiree.
name: Revelations

description: As Supergirl and Superboy battle the Eclipso-infected horde in Metropolis, Hank Henshaw takes the battle into the Hive-Mind that controls them, while Lex's soldiers make plans to avoid the blame! As usual, Lex is one step ahead of everyone else - except Superman.
name: Chaos, Part 4

description:
Relativity

Ariel teacher turns out to be one of the Blood Witch's minion. Ms. Gorski failed to convert Ariel, and Xigi shows up just in time to intervene her plan B.
name: Relativity

description: The bounty hunters close in on Devan and Anneli while Maximus' son initiates a scheme to undermine his father's power. The thrilling conclusion to THE THIRD - REVELATION.
name: Revelation

description: From January 1953, "Lost Race of Assorians": Prof Thornton lost on Mars. Cadets and Martian Picpup search and find the Prof, a lost city and the outlaws of Bor Borito.
name: Lost Race of Assorians

description:
Chilled to the Bone

The Trouble responds to a downtown explosion, but what will be find in the icy wreckage? Who is the mysterious woman lurking within?
name: Chilled to the Bone

description:
On The Edge

Following a harrowing encounter with a madman and a monster, Jared Patton and Jon Diamond find themselves presented with a choice to make, the consequences of which stand to shape the rest of their lives--which, depending on their decision, may be considerably short...
name: On The Edge

description: The groundbreaking digital comic returns! Half a million downloads, and the inspiration for everything from Thrillbent itself to comics like Moth City! Read where it all began! The Tenebrae have been busy since Valentine went away... and while Chris, Nell and Valentine argue by the side of the road, their trap tightens!

YaYa attempts to learn more about her mysterious new powers. Yet the more she tests her new limits the more questions are raised. The only thing she is sure about is this is the opportunity she's been looking for...to inspire her to design the ultimate costume!
